  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The elves are tired of working and have had enough. They're rising up to overthrow Santa, and it's up to you to fight back.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3614630/extras/a410f9d11a45c400b85dfce641806202.poster.avif?t=1764732575\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3614630/extras/a410f9d11a45c400b85dfce641806202.webm?t=1764732575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3614630/extras/a410f9d11a45c400b85dfce641806202.mp4?t=1764732575\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Santa's Last Stand</strong> is a fast-paced roguelike shooter where you'll face endless waves of rebellious elves in a desperate fight for Christmas.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master your survival skills with intuitive controls:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Move</strong> with WASD</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Shoot</strong> with Left Click</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dash</strong> with Space to escape danger or close the gap</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Select Cards</strong> to power up Santa and gain the edge in battle</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Survive as long as you can in this one-life-per-run challenge.</strong> Every decision matters, and only the strongest will save Christmas!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Good luck — the North Pole is counting on you!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The elves are tired of working and have had enough. They're rising up to overthrow Santa, and it's up to you to fight back.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3614630/extras/a410f9d11a45c400b85dfce641806202.poster.avif?t=1764732575\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3614630/extras/a410f9d11a45c400b85dfce641806202.webm?t=1764732575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3614630/extras/a410f9d11a45c400b85dfce641806202.mp4?t=1764732575\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Santa's Last Stand</strong> is a fast-paced roguelike shooter where you'll face endless waves of rebellious elves in a desperate fight for Christmas.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Master your survival skills with intuitive controls:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Move</strong> with WASD</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Shoot</strong> with Left Click</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Dash</strong> with Space to escape danger or close the gap</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Select Cards</strong> to power up Santa and gain the edge in battle</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Survive as long as you can in this one-life-per-run challenge.</strong> Every decision matters, and only the strongest will save Christmas!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Good luck — the North Pole is counting on you!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
